\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa200\f3\fs22\f3\fs22\f3\fs22\lang1025\sl360\slmult1\qj 51.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl360\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls0\li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\sa200\rtlch\af3\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f3\fs22\lang1033\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0{\rtlch\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 Where costs are awarded in a matter, they usually follow the suit and are awarded on a party-party scale.}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s22\sl240\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs33\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up9\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }}{{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0 There are times when a court may impose costs on a more punitive scale such as attorney-client costs or costs }}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0{\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs18\i\loch\f2\fs18\i de bonis propis}{\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs18\loch\f2\fs18 .  But this is done as an exception. See AC Cillers, Law}{\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs18\i\loch\f2\fs18\i  of Cost}{\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs18\loch\f2\fs18 s Third Edition 1997.}}}}
{\*\cs33\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up9\rtlch\af6\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af5\langfe255\hich\f0\fs24\lang1033\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033\rtlch\af2\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 }{\rtlch\af2\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2   The Competition Act deviates from this common law principle in respect of proceedings before this Tribunal.  Section 57(1) provides that each party 
